snippet.title: Home Safety Hotline - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Hearing noises? Seeing things? Call Home Safety Hotline! Our operators are standing by, waiting to give you the answers you need to protect your home from all manner of pests and household hazards. Watch the Home Satey Hotline trailer for this point & click horror game, available now on PC, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation, and Xbox.

#HomeSafetyHotline #Gaming #Horror
